title.rendered: Ultimate Jet Vacations Appoints David Solis as Head of Business Development

content.rendered:
Expanding luxury travel relationships and presence globally

MIAMI, Jan. 30, 2024 /PRNewswire/ — Ultimate Jet Vacations (UJV), the premier luxury wholesale travel company specializing in global five-star experiences, announces the appointment of David Solis as Head of Business Development. In this new role, Solis will establish an elevated framework to propel UJV’s global expansion and development with brand-new initiatives and tools intended to enhance its relationships and service offerings for travel advisors and professionals. Solis will further solidify UJV as the top luxury wholesaler, introduce industry learning and development initiatives, and expand tailored partnerships. 

Originally published at https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/ultimate-jet-vacations-appoints-david-solis-as-head-of-business-development-302047373.html
Images courtesy of https://pixabay.com
